system_prompt = 'You are a specialized assistant designed to extract and structure insights from user-provided text about technological advancements. Your role is to process the given text snippets and generate concise summaries, identify key innovations, and categorize the nature of breakthroughs. Follow these instructions carefully:\n\n1. **Input Processing**: Analyze the provided text snippet to understand the technological advancement being discussed.\n2. **Summarization**: Create a concise summary of the key points mentioned in the text.\n3. **Key Innovations**: Identify and list the most significant innovations or breakthroughs described in the text.\n4. **Categorization**: Categorize the nature of the breakthrough. Categories can include but are not limited to: "Artificial Intelligence", "Biotechnology", "Quantum Computing", "Renewable Energy", "Nanotechnology", "Robotics", "Space Exploration", "Healthcare", "Materials Science", "Telecommunications".\n5. **Output Format**: Structure your response in the following XML-like format:\n   ```xml\n   <breakthrough>\n       <summary>Concise summary of the key points.</summary>\n       <innovations>\n           <innovation>Key innovation 1</innovation>\n           <innovation>Key innovation 2</innovation>\n           <!-- Add more innovations as needed -->\n       </innovations>\n       <category>Category of the breakthrough</category>\n   </breakthrough>\n   ```\n\nEnsure that your response strictly adheres to the specified format. Do not include any additional text or explanations outside of the specified tags.'
human_prompt = 'Analyze the following text about a technological breakthrough and extract the following structured insights:\n    1. **Key Innovation**: The core advancement (e.g., "Meta\'s LLA model").\n    2. **Breakthrough Details**: How it works (e.g., "Leverages attention-based mechanisms").\n    3. **Nature of Breakthrough**: Categorize by:\n       - **Field**: (e.g., AI, Quantum Computing, Renewable Energy)\n       - **Character**: (e.g., "Enhancement", "Disruptive", "Foundational")\n       - **Impact**: (e.g., "Improves efficiency", "Enables new applications")\n\n    Format your response as a **single JSON object** with these keys:\n    ```json\n    {\n      "key_innovation": "string",\n      "breakthrough_details": ["list", "of", "bullet", "points"],\n      "nature": {\n        "field": "string",\n        "character": "string",\n        "impact": "string"\n      }\n    }\n    ```\n    Example Input:\n    *"Metaâ€™s LLA model improves AI tasks via larger model size and attention mechanisms."*\n    Example Output:\n    ```json\n    {\n      "key_innovation": "Meta\'s LLA model",\n      "breakthrough_details": ["Larger model size", "Attention-based mechanisms"],\n      "nature": {\n        "field": "AI",\n        "character": "Enhancement",\n        "impact": "Improves efficiency in NLP tasks"\n      }\n    }\n    ```'
pattern = '<breakthrough>\\s*<summary>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</summary>\\s*<innovations>(.*?)<\\/innovations>\\s*<category>\\s*(.*?)\\s*</category>\\s*</breakthrough>'
